:"Al-Mutaffifin","translation":"Orang-Orang Yang Curang","num_ayah":36,"page":587,"location":"Makkiyah"}},{"id":5859,"surah_id":83,"ayah":11,"page":588,"quarter_hizb":59.5,"juz":30,"manzil":7,"arabic":"الَّذِيْنَ يُكَذِّبُوْنَ بِيَوْمِ الدِّيْنِۗ","kitabah":"الَّذِيْنَ يُكَذِّبُوْنَ بِيَوْمِ الدِّيْنِۗ","latin":"Allażīna yukażżibūna biyaumid-dīn(i).","arabic_words":["الَّذِيْنَ","يُكَذِّبُوْنَ","بِيَوْمِ","الدِّيْنِۗ"],"translation":"yaitu orang-orang yang mendustakan hari Pembalasan.","footnotes":null,"updated_at":null,"surah":{"id":83,"arabic":" المطفّفين","latin":"Al-Muṭaffifīn","transliteration":"Al-Mutaffifin","translation":"Orang-Orang Yang Curang","num_ayah":36,"page":587,"location":"Makkiyah"}},{"id":5860,"surah_id":83,"ayah":12,"page":588,"quarter_hizb":59.5,"juz":30,"manzil":7,"arabic":"وَمَا يُكَذِّبُ بِهٖٓ اِلَّا كُلُّ مُعْتَدٍ اَثِيْمٍۙ","kitabah":"وَمَا يُكَذِّبُ بِهٖٓ اِلَّا كُلُّ مُعْتَدٍ اَثِيْمٍۙ","latin":"Wa mā yukażżibu bihī illā kullu mu‘tadin aṡīm(in).","arabic_words":["وَمَا","يُكَذِّبُ","بِهٖٓ","اِلَّا","كُلُّ","مُعْتَدٍ","اَثِيْمٍۙ"],"translation":"Tidak ada yang mendustakannya, kecuali setiap orang yang melampaui batas lagi sangat berdosa.","footnotes":null,"updated_at":null,"surah":{"id":83,"arabic":" المطفّفين","latin":"Al-Muṭaffifīn","transliteration":"Al-Mutaffifin","translation":"Orang-Orang Yang Curang","num_ayah":36,"page":587,"location":"Makkiyah"}},{"id":5861,"surah_id":83,"ayah":13,"page":588,"quarter_hizb":59.5,"juz":30,"manzil":7,"arabic":"اِذَا تُتْلٰى عَلَيْهِ اٰيٰتُنَا قَالَ اَسَاطِيْرُ الْاَوَّلِيْنَۗ","kitabah":"اِذَا تُتْلٰى عَلَيْهِ اٰيٰتُنَا قَالَ اَسَاطِيْرُ الْاَوَّلِيْنَۗ","latin":"Iżā tutlā ‘alaihi āyātunā qāla asāṭīrul-awwalīn(a).","arabic_words":["اِذَا","تُتْلٰى","عَلَيْهِ","اٰيٰتُنَا","قَالَ","اَسَاطِيْرُ","الْاَوَّلِيْنَۗ"],"translation":"Apabila dibacakan kepadanya ayat-ayat Kami, dia berkata, “(Itu adalah) dongeng orang-orang dahulu.” ","footnotes":null,"updated_at":null,"surah":{"id":83,"arabic":" المطفّفين","latin":"Al-Muṭaffifīn","transliteration":"Al-Mutaffifin","translation":"Orang-Orang Yang Curang","num_ayah":36,"page":587,"location":"Makkiyah"}},{"id":5862,"surah_id":83,"ayah":14,"page":588,"quarter_hizb":59.5,"juz":30,"manzil":7,"arabic":"كَلَّا بَلْ ۜرَانَ عَلٰى قُلُوْبِهِمْ مَّا كَانُوْا يَكْسِبُوْنَ ","kitabah":"كَلَّا بَلْ ۜرَانَ عَلٰى قُلُوْبِهِمْ مَّا كَانُوْا يَكْسِبُوْنَ ","latin":"Kallā bal…rāna ‘alā qulūbihim mā kānū yaksibūn(a).","arabic_words":["كَلَّا","بَلْ ۜ","رَانَ","عَلٰى","قُلُوْبِهِمْ","مَّا","كَانُوْا","يَكْسِبُوْنَ"],"translation":"Sekali-kali tidak! Bahkan, apa yang selalu mereka kerjakan itu telah menutupi hati mereka. ","footnotes":null,"updated_at":null,"surah":{"id":83,"arabic":" المطفّفين","latin":"Al-Muṭaffifīn","transliteration":"Al-Mutaffifin","translation":"Orang-Orang Yang Curang","num_ayah":36,"page":587,"location":"Makkiyah"}},{"id":5863,"surah_id":83,"ayah":15,"page":588,"quarter_hizb":59.5,"juz":30,"manzil":7,"arabic":"كَلَّآ اِنَّهُمْ عَنْ رَّبِّهِمْ يَوْمَىِٕذٍ لَّمَحْجُوْبُوْنَۗ","kitabah":"كَلَّآ اِنَّهُمْ عَنْ رَّبِّهِمْ يَوْمَىِٕذٍ لَّمَحْجُوْبُوْنَۗ","latin":"Kallā innahum ‘ar rabbihim yauma'iżil lamaḥjūbūn(a).","arabic_words":["كَلَّآ","اِنَّهُمْ","عَنْ","رَّبِّهِمْ","يَوْمَىِٕذٍ","لَّمَحْجُوْبُوْنَۗ"],"translation":"Sekali-kali tidak!749) Sesungguhnya mereka pada hari itu benar-benar terhalang dari (rahmat) Tuhannya. ","footnotes":"749) Maksudnya adalah sekali-kali tidak seperti apa yang mereka katakan, yakni bahwa mereka dekat pada sisi Tuhan.","updated_at":null,"surah":{"id":83,"arabic":" المطفّفين","latin":"Al-Muṭaffifīn","transliteration":"Al-Mutaffifin","translation":"Orang-Orang Yang Curang","num_ayah":36,"page":587,"location":"Makkiyah"}},{"id":5864,"surah_id":83,"ayah":16,"page":588,"quarter_hizb":59.5,"juz":30,"manzil":7,"arabic":"ثُمَّ اِنَّهُمْ لَصَالُوا الْجَحِيْمِۗ","kitabah":"ثُمَّ اِنَّهُمْ لَصَالُوا الْجَحِيْمِۗ","latin":"Ṡumma innahum laṣālul-jaḥīm(i). ","arabic_words":["ثُمَّ","اِنَّهُمْ","لَصَالُ